        "fr": "FR_This process allows a user to specify a expected sea level rise over a specified area of interest, returning a GeoTIFF, Shapefile, KML map, or GeoJSON data representing land that would be flooded.",
        "en": "This process allows a user to specify a expected sea level rise over a specified area of interest, returning a GeoTIFF, Shapefile, KML map, or GeoJSON data representing land that would be flooded."
